item.dc:creator: @DePredaTe DePredaTe
item.description:
@DePredaTe wrote:

Ok what i think you are doing (if i’m wrong i’m sorry), Is you are opening it through winrar. You must go to C:\Program Files\MoparScape\HybridScape Then delete everything in that folder. Extract everything in the winrar to the C:\Program Files\MoparScape\HybridScape Then compile your server.
